description: NK favorite DJ is back and he is ripped as ever. Beefy Leo Forte is fast approaching behind with the record of 3-0. Will Leo be able to preserve his winning streak on NK and celebrate by violating DJ's hole and putting him out of commission? Or will DJ slam Leo down, keep him there, and then fuck him like his little bitch? This is the battle of size vs speed. Hang on tight, it's gonna get rough!
title: DJ vs Leo Forte
